{"word":"ἀγέλη","slug":"ἀγέλη","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀγέλη</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἄγω'><el>ἄγω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>a herd</i>, of horses, of oxen and kine, <a href='S:confer, compare'>cf.</a> <el>βούνομος</el>; of swine, <b><a href='S:Hesiod'>Hes.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>any herd</i> or <i>company</i>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>; <a href='S:metaphorically'>metaph.</a>, <el>πόνων ἀγέλαι</el> <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}